title: Ending Is The Beginning-The Mitch Lucker Memorial Show  320k mp3
description:
Ending Is The Beginning-The Mitch Lucker Memorial Show  320k mp3 ak14 What we got...Ending Is the Beginning: The Mitch Lucker Memorial Show is a live video album by American deathcore band Suicide Silence. It was released on CD/DVD/Blu-ray on February 18, 2014. The performance was organized in memorial of founding Suicide Silence vocalist Mitch Lucker, after his death from injuries sustained by a motorcycle accident on November 1, 2012. The performance featured a range of guest vocalists for each of the songs, each of whom were close to Lucker in some way. The title is derived from the title of the opening track of their debut self-titled EP.

The release was dedicated to late vocalist Mitch Lucker and his daughter, Kenadee Lucker.
